description:
**Solace Neurobehavioral and Child Guidance Centre** is one of the best psychiatry clinics in Kerala. We are hiring **Clinical Psychologist - Trainee** (preferably from Kochi).

Location: Kakkanad

**Job description**

* Identify and diagnose psychological, emotional, or behavioral issues;
* Develop and implement treatment plans and therapeutic processes;
* Assesses patients and make recommendations on admission and discharge and on therapeutic activities;
* Maintain an open line of communication with care providers, patients and their family members in order to efficiently address emergencies;
* Assessing clients' risk, considering their mental health and social needs when performing interventions;
* Monitor client progress through regular meetings and checkups;
* Collaborating with other healthcare providers to evaluate the medical and physical condition of clients.
* Help clients define goals and plan action to achieve personal, social, educational, and vocational development and adjustment;
* Ensuring the maintenance and safe storage of accurate program and client records, and all other pertinent documents.

Qualification: MSc Psychology or above

Fresher can apply

Interested candidates please share resumes to solace.hr01@gmail.com

Job Type: Full-time

Salary: ₹10,000.00 - ₹12,000.00 per month

Schedule:

* Day shift
* Morning shift

Work Location: In person
